Nakuru, Kenya: Contrary to fake news going round, Standard Digital has established that not second dam has burst its banks. According to Standard Bureau Chief Alex Kiprotich who is on the ground experts have started draining remaining Patel dams in Solai, Nakuru County so as to allow for inspection of their stability as search for missing people continues. ALSO READ:

